{"tid":826510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 屌你老母 ] 今年國慶煙花用新技術做出笑面和愛心圖案","createTime":"2018-09-18T09:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T12:13:12.000Z","uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4c791e7d0d6cd147b9fcdf31b6d4d87465f0673b","tid":826510,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkcd.com/userfiles/1537258500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcd.com%2Fuserfiles%2F1537258500.jpg&h=7adf44d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年十一國慶煙花匯演，將於當晚9時在維多利亞港上空舉行，全長約23分鐘，主題是團結共融，將由4艘躉船發出31888枚煙花彈。匯演分為8幕，其中第三幕「繽紛人生」以香港樂隊Supper Moment歌曲「橙海」作背景音樂，伴以各色圓球型煙花，象徵每個人都屬於自己，不應被固有框架限制。第5幕「夢想光芒」就利用新技術，首次在圓形煙花上做出笑面和愛心圖案。<br />\n<br />\n匯演由信義玻璃贊助，公司主席李賢義等人介紹。匯演會以團結共融為主題，分為八幕，分別為「黃河奔騰」、「The Greatest Show」、「繽紛人生」、「風光明媚」、「夢想光芒」、「龍騰飛躍」、「紅日之火」、「再創輝煌」;匯演表達的是走出香港、走出國門、走向世界的目標。<br />\n<br />\n統籌煙花匯演公司的行政總裁毛偉誠表示，會在維港上空營造出高1000米、闊300米的煙花銀幕，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>估計總耗資約1000萬港元。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20180918_20180918-170602.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20180918_20180918-170602.jpg&h=c0cee20a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">毛偉誠(右)指今年國慶煙花匯演耗資約1000萬港元</span>"},{"pid":"bd5468146ddcd4a1f5dd57d965545eb37c5499d0","tid":826510,"uid":186,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:39:25.000Z","msg":"燒一千萬"},{"pid":"6bc8fe6364138855a085150312e89306eda5023e","tid":826510,"uid":46151,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:40:31.000Z","msg":"咁有sponsor架嘛<br />\n反而空氣污染仲值得關注"},{"pid":"c098ca25263cf7ae0e6300f8e50f64822d63c4e4","tid":826510,"uid":11598,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:42:11.000Z","msg":"本輯節目獎品獎金非常豐富，其中包括：香港政府送出價值1000萬嘅空氣污染"},{"pid":"6e98a4e7e69fca473ea13d2e81173101e513aa4d","tid":826510,"uid":31841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:44:23.000Z","msg":"supper moment 瀨共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3dd483d7a8ddccf0de34bf68826bfd70771051","tid":826510,"uid":185224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:45:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">贊助</span>"},{"pid":"98065a4656b582093b21941d19bd7c2a2695bfed","tid":826510,"uid":78470,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:48:57.000Z","msg":"浪費錢又污染空氣<br />\n環保狗又唔見佢捉呢啲<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71853cb9fa4366206cf919fa3596104ed1f78d9a","tid":826510,"uid":37586,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:49:00.000Z","msg":"咩國咩慶?<br />\n10月1號香港只有國殤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e97b1eeffc6e03ac2bba8908fdee591e3cd4d0","tid":826510,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:20:32.000Z","msg":"冇山竹牛肉？"},{"pid":"b85e09e23ac0ec3679e7127b90845a60504373bc","tid":826510,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:30:36.000Z","msg":"拎黎派全hk 一人七皮仲好啦！"},{"pid":"541b979d9179c69466e0fba105798beb0d1ad68b","tid":826510,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b85e09e23ac0ec3679e7127b90845a60504373bc","tid":826510,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:30:36.000Z","msg":"拎黎派全hk 一人七皮仲好啦！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:36:58.000Z","msg":"一千萬一人分到一蚊"},{"pid":"a1712586f3184a7ca52927d4859f5b6834dd9f9e","tid":826510,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:38:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆